# Dependencies
node_modules/

# Build output
# dist/ is intentionally COMMITTED: the MCP server is launched straight from
# dist/index.js by Claude Code, so leaving it untracked meant the code being
# executed was ahead of the code under version control. A fresh clone used to
# produce a server that did not match what was actually running.

